# CHORD:
#             quantity   frequency    east-west   east-west   north-south   north-south
# 
#   angular resolution     300 MHz     7.2 mrad       0.41°      4.9 mrad         0.28°
#   angular resolution    1500 MHz     1.4 mrad       0.08°      1.0 mrad         0.06°
